quran[9]{c,v,t}:
  3,1,"Alif – Laam – Meem. (Mavara aya ndemamwe ezvishamiso zvemuQur’aan, uye hapana anoziva zvaanoreva kunze kwaAllah)"
  3,2,"Allah! Laa ilaaha illaa Huwa (Hakuna ane kodzero yokunamatwa kunze kwavo), vanorarama nekusingaperi, muchengetedzi wezvese"
  3,3,"Ndivo (Allah) vakadzikisa Gwaro (Qur’aan) kwauri (Muhammad (SAW)) muchokwadi, richitsigira izvo zvakange zviripo mushure maro. Uye vakatumira Torah neInjeel (Vhangeri)"
  3,4,"Kare, kare, segwara rekutevedzera kuvanhu. Uye vadzikisa Al-Furqaan (Qur’aan senzira yekupatsanura zvakanaka nezvakaipa). Zvirokwazvo, avo vasingatendi muzviratidzo zvaAllah, vachange vane marwadzo akaoma; uye Allah vane simba, vanopa mutongo (vanotsiva)"
  3,5,"Zvirokwazvo, hapana chakavandika kubva kuna Allah, pasi nekudenga"
  3,6,"Ndivo vanokuumbai muzvibereko sekuda kwavo. Laa ilaaha illaa Huwa (Hakuna anekodzero yokunamatwa kunze kwavo (Allah)), samasimba, vane huchenjeri hwese"
  3,7,"Ndivo vatumira Gwaro kwauri (Muhammad (SAW)). Mariri mune ndima dziri pachena, ndidzo midzi dzeGwaro (Ndima dzemitemo), uye nedzimwe dzisina kutsanangurwa (dzisiri pachena). Asi avo vane kurasika mumoyo yavo vanotevera idzo ndima dzisiri pachena mariri, vachitsvaga Fitnah (Miedzo), uye vachitsvaga zvadzinoreva zvakavanzika, asi hapana anoziva zvakavanzika zvadzinoreva kunze kwaAllah. Uye avo vakapihwa ruzivo rwakadzama, vanoti: “Tinotenda madziri (dziri pachena nedzakavanzika), dzese dzinobva kuna Tenzi vedu.” Uye hapana vanotambira mashoko eyambiro kunze kweavo vanonzwisisa"
  3,8,"(Vanoti): “Tenzi vedu! Musaite moyo yedu itsauke (kubva pachokwadi) mushure mekunge matitungamirira, uye mova munotipawo tsitsi kubva kwamuri. Zvirokwazvo, ndimi munopa zvikuru.”"
  3,9,"“Tenzi vedu! Zvirokwazvo, ndimi muchaunganidza vanhu pamwechete pazuva iro risina rupokano mariri. Zvirokwazvo, Allah havaputsi chirangano.”"